text: Jocelyn Wardrop-Moore (born 29 April 1932) is a British alpine skier. She competed in two events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sevenoaks
